flowRoot.flowPara: Tear the pieces on the dotted lines
Place the base tokens far apart and put the flags on them
Place each player next to their color base
Place other business cards down as walls
Players take turns flicking their pieces
If a player hits the other team's flag they pick it up
If a player hits someone on the other team the other player goes back to their base
If a player with a flag is hit they drop the flag where they are and go back to their base
The team to bring the opposing team's flag back to their base wins!
